    "name": "Frost Survival VR",
    "steam_appid": 3054950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a series of unfortunate events, you find yourself surrounded by an ice-covered wilderness. Isolated from the rest of the world, you must rely on your own wits and limited resources to survive these harsh conditions in this <strong>Sandbox Survival in VR</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/187eb5266198547473c0b610a24b57fa.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/187eb5266198547473c0b610a24b57fa.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your main goal is to stay alive, but how?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your Base</strong>: Build a shelter to escape the frost and replenish vital strengths. Enjoy the freedom and construct it however you like. Warm up, protect from wild animals, wait out a snowstorm, store resources, and craft needed equipment there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tools &amp; Weapons</strong>: To survive and fully exploit your surroundings, you will need a variety of tools. Every tool and item has its purpose and durability, which determines how long it can be used until it breaks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt, Craft &amp; Gather</strong>: Hunt wild animals to gain food and resources. Collect items to craft tools, weapons, or clothing necessary for survival.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e7bd2c0746f2b6d8dcfdf3a8b0b325a6.poster.avif?t=1758716138\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e7bd2c0746f2b6d8dcfdf3a8b0b325a6.webm?t=1758716138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/25a0789799430831f18f2b0ef19ab6d0.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/25a0789799430831f18f2b0ef19ab6d0.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surviving isn't easy. Strategizing your moves is crucial to staying alive. Complete essential tasks during daylight and be aware of the darkness, as nighttime brings <strong>lower</strong> <strong>temperatures</strong>. <strong>Weather conditions</strong> are unpredictable and change dynamically, so always be prepared!  Explore a<strong> huge map</strong>, but remember that not every place is safe; some may be inaccessible based on your current gear.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/5fe7f1507c6588b732105e45c3e51a6b.poster.avif?t=1758716138\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/5fe7f1507c6588b732105e45c3e51a6b.webm?t=1758716138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=61 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/bf998fab7fc3ecaaf3efa258d8d1c976.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/bf998fab7fc3ecaaf3efa258d8d1c976.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival isn’t just about staying alive, it’s also about <strong>staying</strong> <strong>sane</strong>. How do you keep your humanity in this frozen hell?  <br>In Frost Survival VR, you must take care of not only your physiological needs, such as hunger, thirst, and keeping yourself warm, but also your <strong>mental health</strong>. If you neglect it, reality may start to blur with illusion.<strong> Fake sounds</strong> and <strong>creatures</strong> will make survival even more challenging. But beware - some figments of your imagination can harm you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/d220ba382b512bb97eda132fe76fdfa3.poster.avif?t=1758716138\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/d220ba382b512bb97eda132fe76fdfa3.webm?t=1758716138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=61 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e36198e47f48c8638c460e8557afa6a2.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/e36198e47f48c8638c460e8557afa6a2.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to survive <strong>alone</strong> or <strong>cooperate</strong> with others in a multiplayer experience. <br>Do you like playing alone? Don’t worry, there are some uncovered secrets scattered across the frozen wilderness that will help you endure. Or you can work together with other players: gather resources, insulate your shelter, and defend against threats like cold, hunger, and dangerous animals. <strong>Shape your survival sandbox experience your way</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/b5b47cc6e0652fdabb36ea5e67aadcae.poster.avif?t=1758716138\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/b5b47cc6e0652fdabb36ea5e67aadcae.webm?t=1758716138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/e6e901f64a49d9c31f64331dc196f11d.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The project is  co-funded by the MEDIA strand of the European Union’s Creative Europe Programme. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/5cf520f50b0968a580a59a5f0cb2b2bd.avif?t=1758716138\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras_big/5cf520f50b0968a580a59a5f0cb2b2bd.avif?t=1758716138 width=800 height=191 /></span></p>",
